# LaTeX build artifacts for documentation figures (regenerated from the .tex sources
# by Scripts/build-doc-figures.sh). Only the .tex source is tracked; the rendered PNG
# referenced by the RST files (Docs/Sphinx/source/_static/<Name>.png) is a build product.
Docs/Sphinx/source/_static/**/*.aux
Docs/Sphinx/source/_static/**/*.log
Docs/Sphinx/source/_static/**/*.pdf
Docs/Sphinx/source/_static/**/*.png
!Docs/Sphinx/source/_static/example_*.png

# Local clang-tidy capture (not part of the project)
/clang-tidy.log
